      "title": "Two ministers to visit Russia tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two ministers will be flying to Russia tomorrow (27) and they will discuss matters including fuel imports during the visit, Minister Kanchana Wijesekara said.",
        "The Minister of Power and Energy revealed this during a press briefing held in Colombo today."
